text: Nikolay Petrushin (born 4 June 1979) is a Russian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Russia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Leninogorsk, Russia
title: Nikolay Petrushin
